Hi Mate,
My name Is Tom. I'm a french guy who lives in Australia for 4years now. I know you doing a lot but I've just went to Batemans Bay 2 days ago and had to come back to sydney as an emergency bushfires as been ordered. You can't imagine how devastating was the situation. It was apocalyptic!!!! I had to pack all my stuff with my wife and my 2years old baby. Tryed to found a way as almost all the roads were closed. It tooks me hours to get back to sydney safe. It will be awesome if you could do something about our firefighters in NSW. They deserve our attention and our support. You've got more than 1million of subscribers... please!!!! It won't take you long to make a short video to support our heroes who fights 24h for our lives!!!! If you don't wanna reply here my Instagram is: mr_leaf_syd
I won't accept any add on my Insta as I'm not looking for that. I'm just a french frog who loves Australia and who wants help my new family.
Hope you'll answer me. And excuse me for my English guys.

snippet.textDisplay: I am so glad to hear you are going to do more with science and education.  you really have a great platform to motivate people to do better by the planet. I started a nonprofit organization in Detroit Michigan and on the Big island of Hawaii, it is an incentive program to motivate any child who would like to participate in bettering themselves and their community. for every good deed they do they get their name added to a drawing and can win a trip to Hawaii and learn and experience paradise through stewardship and community. I would love to figure out a way that we can work together.  local Hawaiian children would love to visit Australia and learn about other awesome places on this planet. and I am sure you coming over here would be amazing for you and your crew.  I look forward to hearing from you. HAPPY NEW YEAR!
